{"tid":1053160,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實所謂嘅曼德拉效應可以咁樣解釋","createTime":"2019-03-08T20:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T02:04:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b754ec588abec8fcf26c4687d0d8c52aa9ac8da","tid":1053160,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T20:45:05.000Z","msg":"有一盞燈，在紅光和黃光之間不斷閃爍，單色閃爍的速度就超過了人眼的極限，那麼有一部分看到的是綠色的，而有一部分人，是黃色色盲，他看不到黃色，所以他看到的一直是紅色的，有一天，燈突然不閃了，停在了紅色上面，前者就討論，為什麼燈變色了？而後者，告訴他們，燈一直都只是紅色的呀！而話曼德拉效應係記憶錯誤嘅人正正就係黃色色盲嘅人，曼德拉效應其實真係存在"},{"pid":"05f2668bbde58c9cf1566503028580dd928d2fd3","tid":1053160,"uid":51171,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T20:51:47.000Z","msg":"一句講晒：明明綠燈轉眼變成紅燈"},{"pid":"a800f0f7e548dfb18e5e1140a8b89494adc96acb","tid":1053160,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309b057a96b11e3359a1cb997d4eefa3cdac8206","tid":1053160,"uid":48579,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T01:51:48.000Z","msg":"最簡單嘅解釋就係啲懵撚記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人嘅記憶本來好唔可靠"},{"pid":"951625ba670fa8aa0b12c6fc4ce0828de8dd7412","tid":1053160,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}